    "faqContent": "Frequently Asked Questions\n\n• How do I reserve a basket?\nBrowse available baskets, select one, choose quantity and pickup time, then confirm.\n\n• What is a surprise basket?\nA surprise basket contains a variety of unsold items from the merchant. Contents vary daily based on availability.\n\n• How do pickup windows work?\nSelect a pickup time window that works for you. Arrive during that time to collect your basket.\n\n• What payment methods are accepted?\nPay directly to the merchant when you pick up your basket (cash or card at the store).\n\n• How do I cancel a reservation?\nGo to the Orders tab, select your order, and tap Cancel.\n\n• Are the baskets the same every day?\nNo, the contents vary depending on the day's unsold items. That's the surprise!",
